Mother couldn't read. No - she used - she used to look at the paper and look at the pictures I think and then she'd finish and perhaps she'd try and read a bit and then she'd have to ask me as I was getting on a bit, what was such a work an
d I would have to look at it and tell her what it was.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 But your father could read?
