\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 Do you know who attended and what type of clothes they wore?
