 and they were paupers graves - there was no - not sufficient insurance to buy grave, you know. Oh I can tell you a funny story about - er - me - er - eventually - about me being chairman of the Cemetery' Committee and finding and bringing one out but tha
t might come out - and when I went that Saturday morning pay the bill - what the dickens going on here - I never seen them bringing them out before - but they was bringing this one out and I tell you what happened. they're two grave papers you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 This is after 1918?
