r all that - we had the - the table piled up with cakes and the best feed we'd ever had for - when the funeral took place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 Were you ever taken out visiting neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14034234 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 Yes. The woman next door along side used to take me on half a day a week - and were I glad to get Weest }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1443249\charrsid7297954 Cemetery}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 .
