No - this was Mrs Evans and she was a grand old soul and her son - er - Willie - he's still alive and - er - she used to take me and him and we walked it to Weest }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1443249\charrsid7297954 Cemetery}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954  and then we walked it back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 Did you never visit relatives?
