No - in - er -off Kay Street. Yes. Well that's the out patients department - and he - he lived opposite in a little pl - I can't just tell you the name of the little street now - but he
 was a book-maker - and I remember him once getting locked up - and he - and they took photographs of him - book-maker taking the - from the roof of the houses opposite, you see, they thought they were mending the slates and they were taking - er - taking
 photographs with the idea of raiding him, you see, they raided him shortly after and - er - put him out of business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 You always went on your own - you didn't go with anyone else?
