 the horses - you know - were very slow. But I tell you what I do remember. I remember the public house trips on a Sunday morning. When the - the - they used to - wasn't coaches like we have today - motor - coaches you know - there was a horse drawn vehic
le and they had three horses in - in the front of this - er - charabanc they called 'em and we as lads used to do the cartwheels while the men - when the men started off so they could throw pennies to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
