\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14034234 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 No - she's a staunch teetotaller 
- we've got a bottle of sherry in our house now it was - it's been here two years and never - no it's never been touched.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 Did she bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14034234 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 No - I don't remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6453660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 Did you grow any yourself?
