\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14034234 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954 No - not at all - no. The only time we had - the only - the only on}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13780532\charrsid7297954 
e we had was a canary and he}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2916006\charrsid7297954  used to sing quite a lot to us and when he died we never got another.
